reviews.review_text:
This recording rules !!  = ) 
 Ive owned a board recording since the summer of 1995 ( Thanks to Chris winston ] of this show   This concert was my 1st

 To some this show was the best of the three at the creek . To others , it was OK , not as great as the other 2 .  To many though, this run at Deer creek was the peak of the summer tour of 194 .  

 What I have to say about this FABULOUS recording , is that it conjures the feeling of being there - 100 % . For the 1st time in 15 years since that concert , i felt what i felt that night  = ) No words can describe the feeling .. Its what we all searched for in the GD experience ( And the next showin Chicago on the 23rd was another High energy affair ]

 The board recording sounds real good . An excellent tape John cutler & Co . made that night ; but this audience recording is amazing ; truly amazing .  I give it the higest rating of 5 * s . Long live this band and its grand music and heritage
